---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="From Bottlenecks to 3X Productivity - Case Study">
	<Header />
	
	<main>
		<section class="section" style="padding-top: 120px;">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
				<a href="/case-studies" class="back-link">← Back to Case Studies</a>
				
				<div class="breadcrumb">
					<a href="/case-studies">Case Studies</a>
					<span>/</span>
					<span>3X Productivity Audit</span>
				</div>
				
				<span class="hero-badge" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Leadership Development Organization</span>
				<h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">From Bottlenecks to 3X Productivity</h1>
				<p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 32px;">How CC3PO helped streamline operations, eliminate inefficiencies, and unlock scalable output — without increasing workload.</p>
				
				<div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 48px;">
					<a href="https://scheduler.zoom.us/carlos-cabrales-iii/3x-strategy-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule Your 3X Productivity Audit →</a>
					<a href="/framework" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn About the Framework</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<!-- Challenge Section -->
		<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
				<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
					<span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--grad); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;">01</span>
					<h2 style="margin: 0;">The Challenge</h2>
				</div>
				<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 24px;">What was holding them back</h3>
				
				<div class="comparison-grid">
					<div class="comparison-card before">
						<h3><span style="color: #ef4444;">✗</span> Before CC3PO</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Manual, repetitive processes slowing down productivity</li>
							<li>Lack of visibility into daily operations</li>
							<li>Inconsistent follow-through across tasks</li>
							<li>Teams working hard but not seeing proportional results</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="comparison-card after">
						<h3><span style="color: #22c55e;">✓</span> After CC3PO</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Streamlined workflows with significantly less friction</li>
							<li>Clear roles and responsibilities across every function</li>
							<li>Improved visibility into day-to-day operations</li>
							<li>More efficient, consistent execution at every level</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<!-- Approach Section -->
		<section class="section" style="background: var(--card);">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
				<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
					<span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--grad); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;">02</span>
					<h2 style="margin: 0;">The Approach</h2>
				</div>
				<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 32px;">The CC3PO method</h3>
				
				<div class="cards-grid">
					<div class="card">
						<span class="phase-number" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">01</span>
						<h3>Identify Bottlenecks</h3>
						<p>Audited all workflows end-to-end to surface where time, effort, and momentum were being lost.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<span class="phase-number" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">02</span>
						<h3>Redesign Systems</h3>
						<p>Simplified fragmented processes, removed unnecessary steps, and built cleaner operational structures.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<span class="phase-number" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">03</span>
						<h3>Implement & Align</h3>
						<p>Rolled out clear accountability frameworks and repeatable systems with team-wide alignment.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<!-- Results Section -->
		<section class="section">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
				<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
					<span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--grad); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;">03</span>
					<h2 style="margin: 0;">The Results</h2>
				</div>
				<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 32px;">The numbers speak for themselves.</h3>
				<p style="color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 32px;">Every gain was achieved without increasing headcount or adding pressure.</p>
				
				<div class="stats-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));">
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-number">3X</div>
						<div class="stat-label">Output increase<br><span style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">Without adding headcount</span></div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-number">60%</div>
						<div class="stat-label">Faster execution<br><span style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">Fewer delays</span></div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-number">100%</div>
						<div class="stat-label">Team alignment<br><span style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">Consistent execution</span></div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-number">Zero</div>
						<div class="stat-label">New hires needed<br><span style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">Removing friction</span></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107, 53, 255, 0.1), rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1)); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin-top: 48px;">
					<p style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin: 0;">"3X Productivity is achieved by removing friction, not adding pressure."</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<!-- Testimonial -->
		<section class="section" style="background: var(--card);">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 700px;">
				<div class="testimonial-card" style="text-align: center; padding: 48px;">
					<p class="testimonial-quote" style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 32px;">"CC3PO helped us streamline operations and significantly increase output without adding headcount. Their structured approach made measurable improvements fast."</p>
					<div class="testimonial-author" style="justify-content: center;">
						<div class="testimonial-avatar">TN</div>
						<div class="testimonial-info" style="text-align: left;">
							<h4>Theresa Nunnally</h4>
							<p>Leadership Development Strategist</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cta-section">
					<h2>Ready to see what 3X looks like in your organization?</h2>
					<p>If your team is working hard but not seeing the results, it's time to rethink how work gets done.</p>
					<div class="cta-buttons">
						<a href="https://scheduler.zoom.us/carlos-cabrales-iii/3x-strategy-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule Your 3X Productivity Audit →</a>
						<a href="/framework" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More About Our Process</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	
	<Footer />
</Layout>